data.description: The home you've been waiting for located on a quiet street! Nice open kitchen with tile floors and custom cabinets. Wood floors throughout. Fenced back yard with tool shed. 2 car garage currently used as additional bedroom the wood shelving stays. Very usable floor plan. All appliances stay including fridge, washer & dryer.
